divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside just after dusk. Looking up in the sky, I spied what I thought was a star. It looked just like a star in the sky. I noticed that it was moving. I thought, "Strange." I watched it as it came across the sky. Then, it came to a dead stop. I assume it then went straight up into space, because it grew dimmer and dimmer, til it was gone.
